cc:Work.dc:title: Flag of Ascension Island
cc:Work.dc:description:
Coat of arms of Ascension Island is traced from the bitmap available at website of government of Ascension Island at http://www.ascension-island.gov.ac/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/Ascension-Island-Flag.jpg
The Government Ensign of the United Kingdom which is used as background of the flag is available as Public Domain at https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:Government_Ensign_of_the_United_Kingdom.svg
